{"tid":112100,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"主人成日搞屋企既神主位","createTime":"2017-02-08T01:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-08T03:04:11.000Z","uid":12190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6f7b735f6f68dad42f27b91ac4b12578949bf40","tid":112100,"uid":12190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:49:42.000Z","msg":"基本上每次佢一搞就大聲嚇佢<br />\n<br />\n但佢走開左一陣又番來搞過<br />\n<br />\n搵支細水槍射佢又試過<br />\n<br />\n都係要搞<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩計仔?"},{"pid":"3a411f64d0477807bb8cb92f07c7f105d74e29b5","tid":112100,"uid":63812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2607f763b144eecf30d55d7c770a1313a8c1b6c5","tid":112100,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"有咩大問題 佢又唔係去冒犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢都係周圍玩姐"},{"pid":"73a660bff7758bfa154d385473c636306f712dde","tid":112100,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:56:26.000Z","msg":"試過見主人呢左係觀音像果度<br />\n勁驚比ar 媽見到"},{"pid":"764ca19fb2d05a11cf64828f45b08557a738af96","tid":112100,"uid":45526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:48:07.000Z","msg":"我都無佢乎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有一燒完香就拎走支竹<br />\n佢都係兩隻腳踏入去望神主牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無乜我都由佢 成日燒香時講多幾句對唔住<br />\n行埋入去打轉我就即刻捉出黎訓話<br />\n<br />\n睇下你屋企人接受程度點啦<br />\n好難教到主人唔入去 我都係最多見我起身屌先肯出番黎"},{"pid":"9ce5697df0ca4bca1a5b539de55e11305bf1b668","tid":112100,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"鬧下佢<br />\n佢地識聽"},{"pid":"f740d5be230f55a0425cb184dd8e407387b8bbdd","tid":112100,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:52:22.000Z","msg":"買個堅有鬼既佛神剋撚住隻貓唔俾佢搞神主牌<img src=\"/assets/fa